## Next Steps for Analytics to Work

To enable analytics data collection on Vercel:

1. Deploy the application to Vercel
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Project Settings → Analytics → Enable)
3. After enabling, the next deployment will activate tracking
4. Verify by checking browser Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`

